类 GeoWithin<V>

    • io.lettuce.core.GeoWithin<V>
  • 类型参数:
    V - Value type.

    public class GeoWithin<V>
extends Object
    Geo element within a certain radius. Contains:
    • the member
    • the distance from the reference point (if requested)
    • the geohash (if requested)
    • the coordinates (if requested)
